\clearpage

\begin{center}
  {\large\bfseries Story Overview}
\end{center}

\indent The story revolves around the character named Roberto, a young Sewist that travels out
of province to find employment opportunities and earn a better living for himself and
his family. One day, he went on a vacation to his hometown in Bicol, Tinambac. Roberto
comes and checks out his home barangay, Tamban for a while to catch up, and repair his
motorcycle to travel around Tinambac. Photography is one of his long lost hobbies, on
his vacation he decided to travel and take photos of memories from his vacations.

\indent Traveling, he realized a lot of things he had missed out on his own home place that he
had never explored. From mundane daily activities to its own simplistic beauty of
provincial experience.

\indent Roberto's roadtrips allow him to see through travel experiences and realizations of
things we missed on our journey, literally and figuratively. At the end of the game, it
would allow you to browse through and check out various photos you have taken
throughout. This would allow you to see the endings of the mini stories you have ended
with the people you have met throughout the journey.

